ygData.messageBody:
I talked to Carver last night, and he is asking you if
you know what type of [meat]? You need to answer his
question. He will not tell you because he doesn't know.
I said "it is HEHE meat." and he reaponded with what he
wants you to do.
"Me wants 20 HEHE meat! you gring me 3 HEHE meat and
recipe and me make you honoraree carver... cleaver cut
skin good!" (or something close to that.) He will not
say any more than that.



--
Cronik <Brethren of ill Omen>
Left Hand of Thule the Pain Bringer
10th Season Troll SK
Bertoxxulous

"Greenbloods jus be Froglok trick. Smash'm and dey
blood same color a Froglok. Me smash'm Greenblood
for Thule. Thule make Cronik big feared. Make
smash'm fun."
